- Add `getSessionRuntimeType(sessionId: string): Promise<string>` to the `Transport` interface in `packages/shared/src/transport.ts`. Implementation in HttpTransport calls `GET /api/sessions/:id` and reads the `runtime` field. Implementation in DirectTransport calls the embedded runtime-registry directly.
- Add `getCapabilities(): Promise<Record<string, RuntimeCapabilities>>` returning the full per-runtime map (the shape already exists on the server via `/api/capabilities`; this surfaces it in Transport).

