Create a new shared abstract `RuntimeAdapter` base class in `packages/relay/src/adapters/` that holds the behavioral logic currently embedded in `ClaudeCodeAdapter`: streaming, delivery, retry, queueing. Runtime-specific concerns remain pure virtual/abstract methods overridden by subclasses.

