Refactor `packages/relay/src/adapters/claude-code/claude-code-adapter.ts` so it extends the shared `RuntimeAdapter` base. Only Claude-specific logic (SDK client construction, claude-native event shape, plugin-aware session open) remains in the subclass. The external name `ClaudeCodeAdapter` is preserved to avoid breaking integrations.

**Target files:**
