Replace the Claude-specific dependency in `apps/server/src/services/relay/adapter-manager.ts` with a runtime-type → adapter-instance map. Dispatch each inbound message via `runtimeRegistry.getSessionRuntimeType(sessionId)` (from Phase 1).

